# [INPUT]: Depends on the root-context e2e image build and the CLI, Hub, and e2e source workspaces.
# [OUTPUT]: Restricts root Docker build contexts to sources required by cross-product end-to-end tests.
# [POS]: Serves as the repository-level Docker context boundary, excluding local binaries, App assets, docs, and VCS state.
# [PROTOCOL]: Update this header when this file changes, then review AGENTS.md
*
!cli/
!cli/**
!hub/
!hub/**
!e2e/
!e2e/**

cli/bin/
hub/bin/
hub/hub
hub/docs/
hub/charts/
hub/dist/
